# Copy to ".env" in this directory (repo root, next to CYRUS.md).
# The dashboard loads it automatically — no need to export vars in the shell.
#
# --- Billing: pick ONE primary path locally ---
# Console API (metered): uncomment and set:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
#
# Claude subscription (Pro / Max) instead: leave ANTHROPIC_API_KEY unset, then log in
# once with Claude Code on this machine (e.g. `claude` in a terminal — OAuth / subscription).
# The CLI/SDK reads ~/.claude under your normal HOME. Do not set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in .env
# if you want subscription auth; otherwise the server strips ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN (see docs).
#
# BRAIN_CHAT_BACKEND=sdk
# DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=
# BRAIN_CHAT_MCP_DB=1
#
# Only if `claude` is not beside your Node binary (see docs/system.md):
# CLAUDE_CODE_EXECUTABLE=/full/path/to/claude
